<p>In the example above, we can select all <code class="highlighter-rouge">p</code> elements excluding those which are <code class="highlighter-rouge">:first-child</code>, <code class="highlighter-rouge">:last-of-type</code> or that have the <code class="highlighter-rouge">highlight</code> class.</p>

